Package: streamy
Title: Inline Contents from Generators into Documents
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Simon", "Couch", , "simon.couch@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5676-5107"))
Description: Given a 'coro' generator instance, inlines text into a document 
    selection in 'RStudio' and 'Positron'. This is particularly helpful for 
    streaming LLM responses into documents.
